            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كَبُرَ مَقْتًا﴾ عَظُمَ بُغْضًا.</h2>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "61:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿صَفًّا﴾ صَافِّينَ صَفًّا.</h2>\n<p>﴿مَرْصُوصٌ﴾ مُتَرَاصٌّ مُحْكَمٌ لاَ فُرْجَةَ فِيهِ، وَلاَ يَنْفُذُ فِيهِ العَدُوُّ.</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "61:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿زَاغُوا﴾ عَدَلُوا عَنِ الحَقِّ، مَعَ عِلْمِهِمْ بِهِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿أَزَاغَ اللَّهُ قُلُوبَهُمْ﴾ صَرَفَهَا عَنْ قَبُولِ الحَقِّ؛ جَزَاءً عَلَى زَيْغِهِمْ.</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "61:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لِمَا بَيْنَ يَدَيَّ﴾ لِمَا جَاءَ قَبْلِي.</h2>\n<h2>﴿بِالْبَيِّنَاتِ﴾ بِالآيَاتِ الوَاضِحَاتِ.</h2>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "61:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمَنْ أَظْلَمُ﴾ لاَ أَحَدَ أَشَدُّ ظُلْمًا، وَعُدْوَانًا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿افْتَرَى﴾ اخْتَلَقَ.</h2>\n<p>﴿يُدْعَى إِلَى الإِسْلاَمِ﴾ يُدْعَى إِلَى الدُّخُولِ فِي الإِسْلاَمِ.</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "61:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿نُورَ اللَّهِ﴾ الحَقَّ الَّذِي جَاءَ بِهِ الرَّسُولُ صلّى الله عليه وسلّم.</p>\n<h2>﴿بِأَفْوَاهِهِمْ﴾ بِأَقْوَالِهِمُ الكَاذِبَةِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مُتِمُّ نُورِهِ﴾ مُظْهِرٌ الحَقَّ بِإِتْمَامِ دِينِهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "61:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لِيُظْهِرَهُ﴾ لِيُعْلِيَهُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿الدِّينِ كُلِّهِ﴾ الأَدْيَانِ المُخَالِفَةِ كُلِّهَا.</h2>"
        },
